Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…没脸见栞大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样貌是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然天海神社有缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该称之为「宿命」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠被神附体了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这个神是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥 弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田河警官 嫌疑人的身份查清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松田寿明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那个邪教团体的干部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还被公安监视过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是IATO的春夏·露谢拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IATO？为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌疑人的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极度衰弱 还出现了记忆障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和在釜谷连续发生的案件有很多相似之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 把你们的资料给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上让他们发给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案件就交给我们 安心享受假期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早料到会变这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么只有我们周围会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在调查这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不要对我们有所隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我知道 也不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为IATO有保密义务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退魔少女吗 我本来觉得很荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但恶灵真的存在对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在追查恶灵的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使不得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论你追查什么案件都与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝不允许你牵连我女儿 缠她们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弥生大人正在疗养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还望两位不要打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带我转告一声 让她保重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定转达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏我有那么多事想问弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 不过没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿杏 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 因为有事所以没能及时和你打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天海神社的神官 吾妻杏美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我阿杏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在对谁说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是昨天来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇缠对吧 我听由麻说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱好是在户外裸奔来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那种爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么娇小可爱的人就是神官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿杏可是当了40年的神官的老手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然又有缠创者出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IATO的情报网真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起这个缠创者 雨音弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她同调的高次元体已经濒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濒死？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是寿命到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能是受了重伤以致无法继续停留在这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨音弥生很快就会不再是缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了 弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进行缠创了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的神已经遍体鳞伤了 不可以乱来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经尽到了缠创巫女的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后就考虑自己的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你的胸大 男人要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为栞的女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小缠身上附着八百万之神的事也知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是头一次听说 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她能否驾驭八百万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢别人耍小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道什么就直接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 昨天弥生真厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么轻松地控制着水龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻你真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你已经作好当退魔少女的心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想过平凡日子 也不想伸吾君为我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.88,0:07:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和恶灵战斗的 只有我和你还有小克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只有当仁不让了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不让大家发现就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真随便
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话 和我一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在啰嗦我就报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在 您找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吧 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,态度随便也能凑合过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种生活态度我学不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头想来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清水的事件和银行事件 那个女孩都在场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原宿和商业街的事件也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩和你有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你消失的原因是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是头一次听说 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她能否驾驭八百万
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们听了之后应该也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天海神社里有缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她们和奈兹一样 也对皇缠有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法蒂玛也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让她加入你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 宗教观相差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们IATO才想要她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你猜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谍报机关和梵蒂冈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷摸摸地在打探什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道我们的来历
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明我们这边也有相应的情报网
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别当我们是远东的岛国就掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人 刚才实在是太对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想顺便问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天海神社在和奈兹战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴眼镜的波霸想都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们法蒂玛也在调查奈兹的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们为什么要介入这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否让我听听您的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 我最喜欢帅哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 其实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 虽然都称为高次元空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上有24个次元之分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不同次元的奈兹 其目的也不尽相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能积极主动地排除即将殃及自己的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到出现「希望」为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望究竟是指
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机到了自然就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 那位美少女拿着的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我观察 你们做了某种仪式处理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想以此实现和神同调对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样称不上是完整的缠创巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早会遇到极限
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们记住这点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是警告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我多管闲事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生啤大杯 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱都被榨干了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不能活得太随便
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的笑容都僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么想吃的 我请你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静养过了 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你受惊吓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生为什么要当退魔少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是天生就具有请神巫女的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得成为缠创巫女是天命使然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们必须做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是和恶灵战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠还早说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创巫女可以通过祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.65,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将神灵纳入其身 并引发奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望之力可以化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化为力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想平凡地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是了不起的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.13,0:12:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话说 我的愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为退魔少女猛揍恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成名人 和好莱坞明星结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及过上超级有钱的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻 你那是烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦恼和愿望不一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创巫女将愿望之力转化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和伸吾君还有妈妈一起普通地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真是赏心悦目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生跟我说直接问你比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15年前 我还是本部的一名新人刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了处理某个案件我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个地方第一次见到了你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两人一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她选择了和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃巫女的身份 和我结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们极其恩爱 甚至让周围的人都很无语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 她对我说过她一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在她回来之前照顾好你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她消失后 我就埋头工作之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想你过得宽裕些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果却去那副惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你那么孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一个不称职的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道伸吾君一直都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我住在奶奶家 只能偶尔与你见面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你一直努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们能在一起生活我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 我会一直相信栞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起相信她 等她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里躺着是手塚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 真的假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手塚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搭讪美女二人组搭得正欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁料她们突然目光呆滞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说详细点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的目标是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了什么不该知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.46,0:15:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很强的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生你就留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波奇 那两个女人去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊桥那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 波奇交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和伸吾君还有妈妈一起普通地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻守一体的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难对付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再往前走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是刑警
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不是普通人能够应付的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也不能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的家人会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为刑警的工作很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这并不意味着你可以让你的家人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会戳人的痛处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很快解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是戳人的痛处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.39,0:17:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想伤害由麻她们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用这种缠创状态战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,栞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这么像妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小缠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了叫你别乱来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望真的很小很平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不值得一提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们一起相信她 等她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的神都吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是八百万之神的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是小缠的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑的形状…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是栞用过的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子在用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望 实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然栞的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开超次元大门的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到小缠的将来 我就有些心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,担心什么 不愿意的话她可以不干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只要那孩子不许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明也不会帮她实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被玷污了 明明是我的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.19,0:23:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会相信她并祈祷她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩还真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.61,0:23:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为奈兹的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和伸吾君被困住了 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身会解除 我的身份就会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 谁来救救伸吾君
